---
title: Peanutty Ground Chicken Stir-Fry with Snow Peas and Peppers
description: This meal is inspired by Thai flavours and is super family-friendly! Crisp veggies and ground chicken is coated with a creamy ginger-peanut sauce. Your flavour-packed plate gets topped with toasted peanuts for a final crunch!
